{"tid":1466724,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"新建議for勇武）放棄機場，由明轉暗","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:53:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T03:39:47.000Z","uid":143542,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b132060e211628f8b0f6d4e083a40647add75636","tid":1466724,"uid":143542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:53:15.000Z","msg":"過左今日，我覺得大家心入面都有條刺係到<br />\n<br />\n同時亦都谷住道氣<br />\n<br />\n我係呢到建議勇武派由明轉暗<br />\n<br />\n以後由和理非主導，勇武派從旁輔助同保護和理飛<br />\n<br />\n然後減少中小型遊行既次數（唔包括特定群體既和理非集會）<br />\n<br />\n以大型遊行為主（30萬人以上）<br />\n<br />\n得閒既時間勇武派由明轉暗，用自己方法抗爭<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">你地係個時做咩我地都唔會割</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n而唔係好似今日係機場入面比鬼玩搞到大家都唔開心"},{"pid":"e97e1a4dbe123018bfb28616fe3c657484ae99b4","tid":1466724,"uid":143542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:53:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49cdd618b333c00bb9e5dbb9135d9d934ef60390","tid":1466724,"uid":143542,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:55:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">記住唔好係镜頭前面做野</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"97b0400b226d68d2dbf7bc72b96c1ea6b411cd6f","tid":1466724,"uid":12146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:56:29.000Z","msg":"鏡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db5c15a8b1ffc837a7f6df4bb83bfa40179ca362","tid":1466724,"uid":275588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:56:45.000Z","msg":"镜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e030217a4ef80c2d9e4392193c5568de77c39b96","tid":1466724,"uid":286670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:02:31.000Z","msg":"[有無人答到我] 好奇一問，點解唔圍港珠澳大橋/高鐵站？?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1466506\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1466506</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1358fe1b6ec464d644be6cdab70e2fb6f6f007af","tid":1466724,"uid":143542,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"db5c15a8b1ffc837a7f6df4bb83bfa40179ca362","tid":1466724,"uid":275588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:56:45.000Z","msg":"镜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:04:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/haUmOQT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhaUmOQT.jpg&h=dd33241b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n手快咁左下面者，唔好咁敏感<br />\n<br />\n用緊gboard速成"},{"pid":"f1ab75b025e57e13fd9fec6ba03b4a0813332ccc","tid":1466724,"uid":143542,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:12:51.000Z","msg":"當我地係弱勢既時候<br />\n<br />\n每一步棋都唔可以行錯<br />\n<br />\n我地而家黎到呢個個係因為對面keep住比機會我地愈滾愈大<br />\n<br />\n我地以後每步棋要愈黎愈謹慎先可以keep住個勢<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係就會變做一子錯，滿盤皆落索"},{"pid":"dfd16db815d592ab6de86e940b0c0a59f4eb791d","tid":1466724,"uid":143542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:16:27.000Z","msg":"就算覺得唔work都討論下點解唔work<br />\n<br />\n大家一齊度下之後應該點做"},{"pid":"3de2feded0ece761fa2c92f9eab53d101fa3f3e3","tid":1466724,"uid":281918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:16:49.000Z","msg":"停機場，休息兩日，All In 818<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1466909\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1466909</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"47014e9023b08c27d908ffb9690f95b9cc9b2306","tid":1466724,"uid":41010,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:17:38.000Z","msg":"第一，請停止在機場勇武，機場係和理非嘅地方，有時間係機場勇武不如做多啲文宣<br />\n<br />\n第二，唔好再捉鬼，唔會捉得晒，喺機場你去做文宣唔駛塞晒條路留返一小部分俾人行就自然會塞，所以啲鬼做乜都冇用，唔該記得你個目的係癱瘓機場<br />\n<br />\n第三，唔好玩膠，今日捉到公安又話遊街又話錫春袋，如果你去機場係認為可以玩玩吓，唔該自己返屋企攝高個枕頭諗清楚"},{"pid":"3051e4309108eb960331050a5975eacf554cf64f","tid":1466724,"uid":4346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49cdd618b333c00bb9e5dbb9135d9d934ef60390","tid":1466724,"uid":143542,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:55:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">記住唔好係镜頭前面做野</span></strong></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:18:08.000Z","msg":"露底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87526d83c94ba50654d93c3834521032a29686f7","tid":1466724,"uid":143542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3de2feded0ece761fa2c92f9eab53d101fa3f3e3","tid":1466724,"uid":281918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:16:49.000Z","msg":"停機場，休息兩日，All In 818<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1466909\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1466909</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:18:35.000Z","msg":"正正係我想表達既野<br />\n<br />\n一係all in 一係暗地行動<br />\n<br />\n幾千到幾萬既小型集會先停一停<br />\n<br />\n唔好比班狗有機會"},{"pid":"ee2c8a4387d00c7afc6c5dac7d7f3f02f013d602","tid":1466724,"uid":143542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3051e4309108eb960331050a5975eacf554cf64f","tid":1466724,"uid":4346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49cdd618b333c00bb9e5dbb9135d9d934ef60390","tid":1466724,"uid":143542,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:55:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">記住唔好係镜頭前面做野</span></strong></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:18:08.000Z","msg":"露底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:19:17.000Z","msg":"屌你老尾睇回覆啦<br />\n<br />\n講左點解喇"},{"pid":"7be5de3d9b5052bc74a6a3a65417e7747bb5c0d8","tid":1466724,"uid":143542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:25:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00c1a48db52e3c19476b736a30220f09a9a60593","tid":1466724,"uid